    • switch_to_modify_form

      public void switch_to_modify_form(javafx.event.ActionEvent event) throws IOException
      *

      RUNTIME ERROR

      This method is used to switch to the modify part form upon click. The actual code for this method is pretty simple and is used to switch the fxml file but once in the modify part controller it took me a minute to figure out how to retrieve the proper part. That is when I decided on having a static member that stores the value of the id of the object that is getting modified so I can access it in another controller

      IOException
